- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a possibility as the paper mentions the characteristic series of the sets. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper discusses linear representations of monoids. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a possibility as the paper deals with the complexity of sets generated by bifix codes and cyclic sets.
